Hello Again! 
I present to you Marty Friedman - Live in Japan Exhibit B DVD Encode. Only the main concert video has been ripped from the original dvd. I didn&amp;#039;t see any sub titles for the interview at the end of it and Marty + Interview guy were talking Japanese, so as such I have not added it. I think the reason is that the DVD was released only in Japan so far if I am not mistaken. Anyway 7gigs (the dvd size) maybe too much for anyone to keep on their pc ( i know it was for me ) so instead I encoded it for my viewing pleasure. 

Encoded For QUALITY 
Video - xh264
Audio - Good old Mp3
Yes there is Chapter Support with Each Song Listed  

